OL,3,CMan jailed after street attack
OL,5,FA Newport man has received a sentence
OL,6,Fof five years in prison after
OL,7,Fassaulting another man in the street.
OL,9,FJordan Rosser, 21, was found guilty by
OL,10,Fa jury of wounding with intent
OL,11,Ffollowing the attack on Caerleon Road,
OL,12,FNewport, at around 1am on 1 March.
OL,14,FHe was cleared of attempted murder,
OL,15,Fpossessing an offensive weapon in a
OL,16,Fprivate place, and being concerned in
OL,17,Fthe supply of class A drugs.
OL,19,FRosser was sentenced at Newport Crown
OL,20,FCourt on Friday 5 December, following
OL,21,Fan eight-day trial held in September.
