OL,3,CMan jailed after street attack
OL,5,FHis co-defendant, an 18-year-old man,
OL,6,Fwas deemed unfit to plead or stand
OL,7,Ftrial; he faced a trial of facts `
OL,8,Falso known as a finding of fact ` to
OL,9,Fdetermine whether the accused
OL,10,Fcommitted an alleged act.
OL,12,FThe man, also from Newport, was proven
OL,13,Fto have carried out an act of
OL,14,Fattempted murder, possession of a
OL,15,Fknife blade/sharp pointed article in a
OL,16,Fpublic place, and being concerned in
OL,17,Fthe supply of cocaine (two counts).
OL,19,FHe received a two-year supervision
OL,20,Forder.
