OL,5,FThe court heard that the victim was
OL,6,Finvolved in an altercation with the
OL,7,Ftwo co-defendants and the injuries he
OL,8,Fsustained in the attack needed
OL,9,Fhospital treatment.
OL,11,FDC John-Paul Velasquez-Cripps, the
OL,12,Fofficer in the case, said: "I hope the
OL,13,Fvictim and his family can now start
OL,14,Fthe process of moving on and
OL,15,Frebuilding their lives after this
OL,16,Fordeal.
