OL,5,F"Fortunately, the victim's injuries
OL,6,Fwere not life-threatening during this
OL,7,Fattack with a knife, but it could have
OL,8,Fbeen significantly worse due to the
OL,9,Fbrutality shown by the aggressors.
OL,11,F"As a service, we continue to speak
OL,12,Fwith young people, in particular, to
OL,13,Feducate them on the consequences of
OL,14,Fcarrying bladed articles.
OL,16,F"Carrying a knife doesn't protect you
OL,17,F` it can make a situation worse. If
OL,18,Fyou know someone who is carrying a
OL,19,Fknife in your area, please report it
OL,20,Fto us immediately.
