OL,5,F"I want to thank the support of the
OL,6,Flocal community, some of whom
OL,7,Fsubmitted vital evidence to us, for
OL,8,Ftheir help in this complex
OL,9,Finvestigation.
OL,11,F"We want our communities to know that
OL,12,Fthis type of behaviour is
OL,13,Funacceptable, and as shown by this
OL,14,Fcase, we will take action against
OL,15,Fdangerous individuals to keep people
OL,16,Fsafe."
